kg.net.bazi.gsb4j

Class Gsb4j

  • java.lang.Object
    • kg.net.bazi.gsb4j.Gsb4j

  • public class Gsb4j
extends Object
    Main entry point to GSB4J application. Besides being a facade class, this class is a place for application wide constant values and utility methods, bootstrap() being the most important one.

    bazi

    • Field Detail

      • GSB4J

        public static final String GSB4J
        Name to distinguish things that belong to Gsb4j. Specifically, it is used to name Guice bindings for types not specific to Gsb4j. For example, Gsb4j has its own binding of ScheduledExecutorService instance which is annotated with this name. This avoids possible conflicts when Gsb4j module is bootstrapped together with other modules that have bindings to the same standard classes.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • API_BASE_URL

        public static final String API_BASE_URL
        Base URL for Google Safe Browsing API. Note that API requests have their own paths to be resolved relative to this base URL. This URL has a trailing slash.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • durationToMillis

        public static long durationToMillis(String duration)
        Parses and converts duration strings from API to milliseconds. API returns durations in seconds with up to nine fractional digits, terminated by 's' like "593.44s".
        Parameters:
        duration - duration string to parse
        Returns:
        duration in milliseconds
